{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I could not believe-- and my father had to go back, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I could not believe that she is there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I petted her, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And she didn't utter a sound.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Around maybe two weeks later, she beckoned me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And she said something to me, which I don't really remember-- something that she is preparing me for something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "There was, around the corner, when they ran up-- around the corner, entering the little kitchenette, there was like a narrow cupboard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It was a very high, narrow, dark brown, solid cupboard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And in this cupboard, one of drawers-- I could reach up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And I was very small, so it was not on the lower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "But it was somewhere on the higher-- there was a false, little drawer, which I assume my father-- I would-- or it was the-- or my father made-- a very, just, you know, literally sort of-- sort of touching-- you know, just very small.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And there was a hook-- just you had to put your hand inside around there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "On the left-hand side, there was like a little hook there that if you-- it was not visible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "You couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "But if you unhooked that, the whole-- this-- it all dropped onto the next one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "So whatever bits and pieces there was, it was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Lilka said to me, you think that I didn't know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that it was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew all along that it was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just could not believe it-- that she could, at her age-- what was she-- 8, 8 and a 1/2 --that she could-- that she took-- that she understood.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That she took.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later on they started to bribe her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, they said, we give you-- they changed, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
